{
  "_comment": "World config = the instance layer. The plugin ships English defaults (world.default.json); this file OVERRIDES any subset of them. You only need the keys you actually change. To activate: copy to world.json (same folder) and edit. This example shows a Hungarian instance.",

  "_comment_sections": "If you localize section names here, your learnings.md / system learnings.md section headers MUST match these strings exactly (the engine splits on them).",

